  <thing id="g5CPipeMd" name="Acorn of the Pipemold Flower [endowment]" description="These acorns are potent indeed. Stored correctly by an experienced herbalist in a vial of vinegar, the acorn becomes brittle and hard. Simply swallowing it is enough to recover 1d6 hit points, although doing so is a fairly unpleasant task and requires the  recipient to swallow it whole.\n\nSkill Wisdom (Medicine) 15; preparation time 1 action" compset="Gear">
